OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774379485
OL,3,CThe US controls the skies, but Iran
OL,4,Chas a tight grip on vital oil and gas
OL,5,Croute
OL,7,FMuch of the world's energy supply
OL,8,Fdepends on the gigantic tankers being
OL,9,Fable to use the narrow Strait of
OL,10,FHormuz. ITV News' Economics Editor
OL,11,FJoel Hills takes a look at how it's
OL,12,Fbeing controlled
OL,14,FThe war in the Gulf has caused the
OL,15,Fbiggest disruption to the global
OL,16,Fsupply of oil and gas the world has
OL,17,Fever seen.
OL,19,FIn the Strait of Hormuz, more than
OL,20,F1,200 ships are stranded, unable to
OL,21,Fleave.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774379485
OL,3,CThe US controls the skies, but Iran
OL,4,Chas a tight grip on vital oil and gas
OL,5,Croute
OL,7,FThe United States and Israel have
OL,8,Fcomplete control of the skies, but
OL,9,FIran is calling the shots over who
OL,10,Fpasses through one of the world's most
OL,11,Fimportant shipping lanes.
OL,13,F"Iran seems to have an effective
OL,14,Fblockade in place and is consolidating
OL,15,Fcontrol, effectively routing vessels
OL,16,Fvia its territorial waters, providing
OL,17,Fselective permission to vessels
OL,18,Faffiliated with India, China and
OL,19,FPakistan," says Michelle Bockmann, a
OL,20,Fmaritime intelligence analyst at
OL,21,FWindward.
OL,26,@uD@AOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774379485
OL,3,CThe US controls the skies, but Iran
OL,4,Chas a tight grip on vital oil and gas
OL,5,Croute
OL,7,FOn a normal day at this time of year,
OL,8,Faround 120 vessels pass through the
OL,9,FStrait.
OL,11,FTraffic is currently down 97%.
OL,13,FBut as Windward points out, some ships
OL,14,Fare still getting through.
OL,16,FPine Gas, an Indian flagged ship, made
OL,17,Fits way through the Strait, while many
OL,18,Fothers remained stranded. Source:
OL,19,FMarinetraffic.com
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774379485
OL,3,CThe US controls the skies, but Iran
OL,4,Chas a tight grip on vital oil and gas
OL,5,Croute
OL,7,FThis morning, the Pine Gas tanker made
OL,8,Fthe passage, carrying liquefied
OL,9,Fpetroleum gas to India.
OL,11,FAccording to tracking data from
OL,12,FMarineTraffic.com, unusually, it
OL,13,Fsailed north of Larak Island, deep
OL,14,Finto Iranian waters.
OL,16,FThe suggestion is that Iran gave it
OL,17,Fsecurity clearance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774379485
OL,3,CThe US controls the skies, but Iran
OL,4,Chas a tight grip on vital oil and gas
OL,5,Croute
OL,7,FTwenty-four ships in the Strait have
OL,8,Freported being hit by drones or drone
OL,9,Fdebris since the conflict began three
OL,10,Fweeks ago.
OL,12,FSome attacks have caused significant
OL,13,Fdamage; many others have not. Cargo
OL,14,Fships and bulk carriers have been
OL,15,Ftargeted, as well as oil tankers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774379485
OL,3,CThe US controls the skies, but Iran
OL,4,Chas a tight grip on vital oil and gas
OL,5,Croute
OL,7,FAmid the chaos, Iran's oil exports
OL,8,Fremain relatively steady. Ninety per
OL,9,Fcent of its oil passes through
OL,10,Fterminals at Kharg Island - these
OL,11,Fsatellite images from recent days show
OL,12,Ftankers are still loading there.
OL,14,FPresident Trump has reportedly
OL,15,Fconsidered occupying Kharg Island. He
OL,16,Fhas also threatened to target power
OL,17,Fstations in Iran if it does not reopen
OL,18,Fthe Strait of Hormuz by Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774379485
OL,3,CThe US controls the skies, but Iran
OL,4,Chas a tight grip on vital oil and gas
OL,5,Croute
OL,7,FSir Richard Barrons, a retired senior
OL,8,FBritish Army officer who served as
OL,9,FCommander Joint Forces Command from
OL,10,F2013 to 2016, warns there is no
OL,11,Fmilitary solution to the situation in
OL,12,Fthe Strait of Hormuz and that striking
OL,13,Fcivilian power plants would lead to a
OL,14,Flarge loss of life.
OL,16,F"If (Trump) does that, he must know
OL,17,Fthat he will be killing tens, possibly
OL,18,Fhundreds of thousands of people who
OL,19,Fare denied power and therefore water,
OL,20,Ffood and everything else," Sir Richard
OL,21,Ftold ITV News.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@EpmxD@Kpn|D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774379485
OL,3,CThe US controls the skies, but Iran
OL,4,Chas a tight grip on vital oil and gas
OL,5,Croute
OL,7,F"And I think President Trump will have
OL,8,Fto think very hard before he takes a
OL,9,Fstep like that, because many people in
OL,10,FEurope - and I think in the US - would
OL,11,Fcall it a war crime."
OL,13,FIt is still not clear where this
OL,14,Fconflict is heading.
OL,16,FIran cannot win a conventional war,
OL,17,Fbut it is waging an economic war -
OL,18,Fwith some success.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
